er Thraning."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "4013412c7cd8c6b6758059116fbbfd567aa65cc5b200f97fae35b732ae5af383"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-04-01T17:42:59.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Skarpskodde advokater g\u00e5r n\u00e5 til Stj\u00f8r- og Verdal tingrett for \u00e5 f\u00e5 stanset nedleggingen av byskolen i Levanger."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1135527.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Skoleadvokat5"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/eb63ff43ed6304f15a7113a93f092239e20c9482.jpg?594b9f8e"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Skolenedleggelse til retten -adressa.no", "M\u00e5 forklare seg", "Har d\u00e5rlig tid", "Rolig r\u00e5dmann"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "eb63ff43ed6304f15a7113a93f092239e20c9482"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "education"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["kommune", "stanse nedleggingen", "rettssak", "sak", "skole"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["ertsaas", "lindsetmo", "stj\u00f8r", "christensen", "hans aalberg"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["levanger", "verdal", "steinkjer", "norge"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["odd thraning", "ola stene", "anders kj\u00f8ren"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1135527.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Skoleadvokat5"}, {"field": "og-locale", "value": "nb_NO"}, {"field": "og-site-name", "value": 